548
00:39:01,086 --> 00:39:02,266
Got it memorized?

549
00:39:02,266 --> 00:39:06,286
Yes, Mother. They are truly shameless.

550
00:39:13,867 --> 00:39:16,147
I know Yi Ren well.

551
00:39:16,147 --> 00:39:20,066
Though reasonable normally,
he's extremely concerned with face.

552
00:39:20,066 --> 00:39:23,707
I know you've got tricks,
but you need to be careful.

553
00:39:23,707 --> 00:39:26,707
As my youngest son,
don't get injured by the eldest.

554
00:39:26,707 --> 00:39:28,967
Or I'll be very sad.

555
00:39:29,447 --> 00:39:31,654
Don't worry, Mother.

556
00:39:32,166 --> 00:39:34,622
- Do your best.
- Okay.

557
00:39:35,546 --> 00:39:40,827
Remember. If you can't win, surrender.
